schools.name: Galileo School Of Math And Science

data.description: Great, like new home in a quiet neighborhood!  Move-in ready with a complete remodel and all new fixtures and appliances!  Perfect floorplan with a formal living room plus neat family room with fireplace on the main.  Must see the main level laundry and large pantry with convenient 1/2 bath off the family room!  New garage door.  4 bedrooms upstairs ~ the Master has walk in closet and 3/4 bath!  Large fenced yard and storage shed.  Covered front porch for sitting & watching the world go by as well as protection from the elements.
